definition: mark/sign/label/to mark with a symbol, label, lettering etc/to bear (a brand name, registration number etc)/prize/award/bid/target/quota/(old) the topmost branches of a tree/visible symptom/classifier for military units
inscribed bamboo stick (used in divination, gambling, drawing lots etc)/small wood sliver/label/tag

sentences.english: I took a picture so you can see the label.
sentences.chinese: 我拍了張像片所以你們能夠看到這個標籤。

sentences.english: She needs the tickle of cashmere to enchant for the ages.
sentences.chinese: 她需要開士米羊毛的標籤來增加年齡的魅力。

sentences.english: The stewards had stuck sticky labels on the cargo.
sentences.chinese: 乘務員已經將粘性標籤粘貼在貨物上了。

sentences.english: With quickset label, easy to inquire about information.
sentences.chinese: 插條式標籤，便於資料查詢。

sentences.english: Please note that the product label bears the Clariant mark as shown in the above sample.
sentences.chinese: 請注意產品標籤上的科萊恩標誌，如上圖樣本所示。

sentences.english: It has 13 pockets with tabs and an elastic-cord closure.
sentences.chinese: 他有13個帶標籤的隔層和一個彈性繩釦。

sentences.english: Go back to the configuration tool and find the Authentication tab.
sentences.chinese: 回到配置工具，並找到驗證標籤。

sentences.english: The font tag has two required attributes and one optional one. They map directly to the three parameters in the java.awt.Font class
sentences.chinese: font標籤有兩個必需的屬性和一個可選屬性。

sentences.english: The labeler shall operate with a minimum of operator involvement.
sentences.chinese: 貼標籤機應當在最少的操作員介入條件下運行。

sentences.english: This is an open label, randomized, comparative, multi-center study.
sentences.chinese: 這是一個開放的標籤，隨機，對照，多中心研究。

sentences.english: Each picture is marked with descriptive tags, making it easy to find what you’re looking for.
sentences.chinese: 每幅圖片都帶有描述標籤，便於你查找。

sentences.english: We will replace this simple do-nothing application with the code in Listing 2, which does a whole lot.
sentences.chinese: 下面我會使用列表2中的代碼來代替這個空白標籤。

sentences.english: Please fasten these tags on your hand-carry luggage.
sentences.chinese: 請把這些標籤系在您的手提行李上。

sentences.english: Who you are is beyond these little labels.
sentences.chinese: 你的本質與這些小標籤無關。

sentences.english: The 4D adjustable printer head is convenient for printing labels of different materials.
sentences.chinese: 四向位可調式打印頭，便於配合不同標籤材質的應用。
